   "source": [
    "To investigate whether a country’s economic development is associated with how students use ChatGPT for schoolwork, we conduct an exploratory data analysis (EDA) focusing on three main components:\n",
    "\n",
    "   1. The composition of our filtered student sample across countries\n",
    "\n",
    "   2. The distribution of country-level economic development (GDP per capita, PPP)\n",
    "\n",
    "   3. The relationship between economic development and students’ ChatGPT usage behavior\n",
    "\n",
    "Because the survey dataset contains responses from a wide range of participants, we first restrict the dataset to match our target population: full-time undergraduate students enrolled in on-campus, in-person courses.\n",
    "\n",
    "We then merge the survey data with country-level GDP per capita (PPP) from the World Bank to explore cross-country differences in economic development."
   ]
